result: Queestão 45) Irere, my crossroad of the Cariri backwoods, Irere, my companion, where is guitar? Where's my good? Where's Maria? Oh sad luck that of guitarist Cantadô! Ah! Without the guitar in which he sang his love, ah! Your whistlle is your fluite of Irere: May your backwoods fluite when whistlle, ah! We suffer without want! Ah! Your corner gets to the back of the backlands, ah! Like a breeze softening the heart, ah! Ah! Irere, loose your corner! Sing more! Sing more! To Alembá Cariri! VILLA-LOBOS, H.
